Important note

After moving partial paths, you will probably need to update this test:

test-overrides-and-preserve-policy.sh

because it currently includes older partial paths like:

{% include "partials/install-mode-text.ks.j2" %}

Those will need to become the new paths, like:

{% include "partials/20-install-mode/text.ks.j2" %}

So the best next move is:

First create the new minimal partials and update the three minimal KS templates. Then run pxe-content-test all.

Once that passes, we move to small-disk.